    <h1 class="gem-c-title__text govuk-heading-l">
      You cannot use this service
    </h1>

    <p class="govuk-body">This service is for sponsoring a child fleeing Ukraine, who is not travelling with or joining their parent or legal guardian in the UK.Â </p>

    <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-font-weight-bold">To apply the child must:</p>

    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>be under 18</li>
      <li>have been living in Ukraine on or before 31 December 2021</li>
      <li>be applying to travel to the UK either without a parent or legal guardian, or not joining them in the UK</li>
      <li>have written consent from their parent or legal guardian</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-font-weight-bold">To apply you (the sponsor) must:</p>

    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>be over 18</li>
      <li>have permission to live and work in the UK for at least 3 years</li>
      <li>care for the child in the UK for at least 3 years, or until they turn 18 and you have hosted them for at least 6 months</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="govuk-body">If you want to sponsor an adult fleeing Ukraine, they can apply for a visa straight away using your personal details.</p>
    
